Definition: make clear by special emphasis and try to convince somebody of something
Example: drive home a point or an argument; I'm trying to drive home these basic ideas
Synonyms: ram_home, press_home, stress, make, clear, by, special, emphasis, and, try, to, convince, somebody, of, something, drive, home, a, point, or, an, argument, I, m, trying, these, basic, ideas
Frame: 8
Category: verb.communication
